						               													<description>Translation from the website:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every year the wizards compete to become the Masterwizard. This year the tournament is held in the forest of a thousand roads. There the wizards will have to prove themselves by bringing their new students to the magical destination. Do you dare taking on this challenge and play the game? Your students aren't allowed to use magic, so the result of the tournament is in your hands. By acquiring the right magic cards your students can travel quickly or your opponents students can be hindered.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;By smartly and tactically using your magic powers, you can easily reach the destination. With Tover je Toverweg the takes the first steps in the magical world of boardgames. The structure and setup offer the right balance between options and ability for the youngest players. With 4 different game boards, accessories and extensive variants the game is a challenge for young as well as old (and even grown-ups). The game grows along with the development of the spacial view.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
